{"id":"14e6362c-f3cc-4659-b2b5-74e196d34e1c","name":"Five Nights at Miko's 2","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">It's bigger, it's badder, it's too much for John Touhou! The FNAF parody returns in this sequel featuring more characters, improved mechanics, and more! Didn't play the original? Let me break it down for ya: Five Nights at Miko’s is a Touhou themed FNAF parody where you work the night shift as a security guard for Miko Borgar. Can you survive five nights?<br><br><img draggable=\"true\" class=\"css-9pa8cd\" style=\"\" alt=\"Image\" src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EuxqrseWYAI8guk?format=jpg&amp;name=4096x4096\"><br>Starring:<br><br>Reimu Hakurei</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Marisa Kirisame</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Sakuya Izayoi</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Youmu Konpaku</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Withered Junko</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Koishi Komeiji</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Cirno</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Clownpiece</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Aunn Komano</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Kogasa Tatara</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Rumia</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">and the Zun returning as Phone Guy</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><br><img draggable=\"true\" class=\"x85a59c x193iq5w x4fas0m x19kjcj4\" style=\"\" alt=\"No photo description available.\" src=\"https://scontent-sea1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t39.30808-6/240515641_2894649097514104_3518227708480612360_n.jpg?_nc_cat=100&amp;ccb=1-7&amp;_nc_sid=833d8c&amp;_nc_ohc=9NIvliA72VYQ7kNvgHd7Hbs&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-sea1-1.xx&amp;_nc_gid=AY8w8vF43qAWiZyQRX1Kjye&amp;oh=00_AYDfXkXnr20UpTd4KMtRiQaaaYaUmvlCUQKGNfhhDQR6hA&amp;oe=67377051\">Avatar by <a href=\"https://www.reddit.com/r/touhou/comments/td1pub/kogasa_fnaf/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">u/us_EL_ess</a></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"65da3d3e-dc86-447f-9987-6f03aa60cd64_8f530d27-0e8c-4963-9dd9-72be9d8